  "title": "Delivery driver cum handyman",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Permanent Position: Delivery man/ Handyman</li>\n  <li>Working hours: Mon - Fri (8.30AM - 6PM)</li>\n  <li>Assist in the day-to-day operations of delivering materials or equipment to various company outlets in Singapore.</li>\n  <li>Includes Picking and Packing, as well as Loading and Unloading duties.</li>\n  <li>Involved in receiving of incoming goods, data entry and keeping track of stocks\\</li>\n  <li>Perform simple ad hoc handyman tasks as required at company outlets.</li>\n  <li>Any other tasks as assigned.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Physically fit</li>\n  <li>Positive attitude</li>\n  <li>Strong sense of responsibility and good team player</li>\n  <li>Class 3 Driving License</li>\n  <li>Willing to work OT when required</li>\n</ul>",
